                    "line_text": "Dit l’évangile de saint Jean :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sur la tête du paysan,\nRite profond, vaste symbole,\nLe prêtre, étendant son étole,\nDit l’évangile de saint Jean :"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "« Au commencement était le Verbe",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "« Au commencement était le Verbe"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "S’épanchant en ondes de claire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Vérité sur l’humaine erreur,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Lavant l’immondice et l’horreur,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Et la luxure et la colère,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "S’épanchant en ondes de claire,\nVérité sur l’humaine erreur,\nLavant l’immondice et l’horreur,\nEt la luxure et la colère,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Et les sept péchés, et d’un flux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Tout parfumé d’odeurs divines,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Rafraîchissant jusqu’aux racines",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "L’arbre du bien, sec et perclus,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et les sept péchés, et d’un flux\nTout parfumé d’odeurs divines,\nRafraîchissant jusqu’aux racines\nL’arbre du bien, sec et perclus,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Et déracinant sous sa force",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "L’arbre du mal et du malheur",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Naguère tout en sève, en fleur,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "En fruit, du feuillage à l’écorce.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et déracinant sous sa force\nL’arbre du mal et du malheur\nNaguère tout en sève, en fleur,\nEn fruit, du feuillage à l’écorce."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "O Jean, le plus grand, après l’autre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Jean, le Baptiste, des grands saints,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Priez pour moi le Sein des seins",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Où vous dormiez, étant apôtre !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "O Jean, le plus grand, après l’autre\nJean, le Baptiste, des grands saints,\nPriez pour moi le Sein des seins\nOù vous dormiez, étant apôtre !"
        },
        {
